#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.10/site-packages/numpy/lib/arrayterator.py:docstring
#: of numpy.lib.arrayterator.Arrayterator:2
msgid "Buffered iterator for big arrays."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.10/site-packages/numpy/lib/arrayterator.py:docstring
#: of numpy.lib.arrayterator.Arrayterator:4
msgid ""
"`Arrayterator` creates a buffered iterator for reading big arrays in small "
"contiguous blocks. The class is useful for objects stored in the file "
"system. It allows iteration over the object *without* reading everything in "
"memory; instead, small blocks are read and iterated over."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.10/site-packages/numpy/lib/arrayterator.py:docstring
#: of numpy.lib.arrayterator.Arrayterator:9
msgid ""
"`Arrayterator` can be used with any object that supports multidimensional "
"slices. This includes NumPy arrays, but also variables from Scientific.IO."
"NetCDF or pynetcdf for example."
msgstr ""

